---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy — Global Wealth Portfolio" description="Your data stays on your device. We don't collect anything.">
  <section class="container-page page-section pt-3xl pb-2xl max-w-3xl">
    <p class="text-caption-mono text-body mb-xs">Privacy</p>
    <h1 class="text-display-lg mb-lg">Your data stays on your device.</h1>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      Global Wealth Portfolio is built on a simple principle: <strong>your financial data is yours</strong>.
      The entire app runs in your browser. We don't have servers storing your
      investments, expenses, or goals. We don't use analytics that can identify you.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">What we don't collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-lg space-y-xs text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      <li>Your investment holdings</li>
      <li>Your expense records</li>
      <li>Your financial goals</li>
      <li>Your EMI / loan information</li>
      <li>Your uploaded bank statements (they never leave your device — OCR runs locally)</li>
      <li>Your name, email, or any personal identifier</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">How your data is stored</h2>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      All your portfolio data is stored in your browser's <code>localStorage</code>.
      It never leaves your device. If you clear your browser data, your portfolio
      will be lost — please use the JSON export feature regularly to back up.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">Bank statement OCR</h2>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      When you upload a bank statement image, the OCR (text recognition) runs
      entirely in your browser using Tesseract.js. The image is never uploaded
      to any server. After the OCR finishes, you can delete the image from your
      device — the parsed text and transactions are stored only in your browser.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">Third-party services</h2>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      The app loads fonts from Google Fonts and uses no other third-party
      tracking, advertising, or analytics services. The only network requests
      are to load the app itself.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body">
      Questions? Email <a href="mailto:privacy@globalwealthfolio.com" class="text-link hover:underline">privacy@globalwealthfolio.com</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
